<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741035>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Macrobrachium tenuipes sp. nov. holotype male (FU, 2018-11-25-01). A, Entire animal, lateral view; B, first pereiopod; C, second pereiopod; D, fingers of second pereiopod; E, third pereiopod; F, fifth pereiopod." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3741035/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741037>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Macrobrachium tenuipes sp. nov. Paratype male (FU, 2018-11-25-02). A, antennule; B, antenna; C, mandible; D, maxillule; E, maxilla; F, first maxilliped; G, second maxilliped; H, third maxilliped; I, telson." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3741037/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741039>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. A and B, Macrobrachium tenuipes sp. nov., cephalothorax and cephalic appendages, lateral view and dorsal view; C and D, M. superbum, cephalothorax and cephalic appendages, lateral view and dorsal view; E and F, second pereiopod and fingers of second pereiopod of M. superbum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3741039/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741041>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. A and C, Macrobrachium tenuipes sp. nov., lateral view and dorsal view; B and D, M. superbum, lateral view and dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3741041/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3741031>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Bayesian inference phylogram of palaemonids based on concatenated COI and 18S rRNA sequences. Numbers at nodes represent posterior probability." ;
